          "details": "Ensure that SIMATIC WinCC, SIMATIC WinCC Runtime Professional and SIMATIC PCS 7 stations communicate via encrypted channels (i.e. activate feature \u201cEncrypted Communication\u201d in SIMATIC WinCC V7.3 or newer and SIMATIC PCS 7 V8.1 or newer). Enabling \u201cEncrypted Communication\u201d completely mitigates the vulnerability.",
